narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: L2 Spanish is an intense course to follow the baseline Spanish knowledge of L1 that challenges you with readings, film, class activities, etc. It is a great course that I thoroughly enjoyed and I would recommend it to a fellow student. Great preparation for an L3/L4 intensive summer or any kind of study abroad--or just life.
I enjoyed the course and would recommend it to another student.
I would recommend this class. It is decently easy, you just need to ACTUALLY do your homework becasue it is graded and practice speaking and listening with friends. Also, be on time to class!
